Constructor Detail

Reader

public Reader(File config)
Constructor for objects of class Reader. Creates a scanner object reads through the 8 lines of the configuration file and stores the information on each line in an array list for each type of space. This information will be accessed by the board class.

public ArrayList<Integer> getBoardDimensions()
getBoardDimensions - returns the JStack array storing the infromation from the configuration file. This includes each dimension of the board

Returns:

getEmptyArray

public ArrayList<Integer> getEmptyArray()
getEmptyArray - returns the Empty array storing the infromation from the configuration file. This includes the probability a space is of the type Empty

Returns:
ArrayList - first element is the probability

getHoldArray

public ArrayList<Integer> getHoldArray()
getHoldArray - returns the hold array storing the infromation from the configuration file. This includes the probability a space is of the type Hold, as well as the range of the multiplier for the Hold.

Returns:
ArrayList - first element is the probability, the second is the upper bound of the multiplier, the third is the lower bound of the multiplier

getTreasurePotAArray

public ArrayList<Integer> getTreasurePotAArray()
getTreasurePotAArray - returns the TreasurePotA array storing the infromation from the configuration file. This includes the probability a space is of the type TreasurePotA, as well as the number of treasure pieces to remove and the number of removals.

Returns:
ArrayList - first element is the probability, the second is the number of peices to remove, the third is the number of removals

getTreasurePotBArray
